## What was broken and exactly why

| Bug | Root cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| Random numbers | `FlagshipBillboard` was reading `block.fontSizePx` before it was set — showed uninitialised float | `BitmapAnalyzer.analyze()` now runs before anything else |
| Wrong boundary | Coordinates transformed through 3 different scaling pipelines that didn't match | `PixelCopy` captures at glView size, ML Kit runs on same size bitmap — coordinates are 1:1, no scaling needed |
| Overlay rotates with phone | `makeBillboard()` copied camera view matrix columns | `placeBlocks()` now takes rotation from `plane.getCenterPose()` — completely independent of camera |
| Floating | Quad was a camera-facing billboard | Quad lies flat in XZ plane, Y=up matches plane normal — sits flush on surface |
| Too many broken layers | 8 classes all calling each other with stale data | Collapsed to 5 classes with one clear data flow: `TextBlock` carries everything |